title: Rare Hits of The 80's Vol 61
description:
Did anyone miss me and the music I post? whether you did or not, it's time to end this long hiatus! (huummm I sounded like B-movie!). Since noone in my absence continued what I had started. I guess I need to get active again.  

Here you are and part 61 of this beloved obscure 80s compilations. I hope you do
find some cool songs here.
